      <a class="twitter-timeline" data-lang="ja" data-theme="light" href="https://twitter.com/genron_sf_fun?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">Tweets by genron_sf_fun</a>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <a class="twitter-timeline" data-lang="ja" data-theme="light" href="https://twitter.com/genronschool?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">Tweets by genronschool</a>
    </div>
